title: Dark Time [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
After many studies of teleportation of objects in space, scientists first tried it with animals, and then began to move people.
At first everything was just fine. A quick move saved both time and money. But as time went on, the portals began to open that led to zombies and monsters. It became dangerous as the portals go both ways. But the technology of teleportation is here to stay.
People went the easy way and decided to move the residents out of dangerous areas and create teams to destroy the unwanted guests.
You are the commander of one such command to destroy monsters. Constantly clean the monsters out of the zone and take care of the rest of the inhabitants.

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 mb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 655 mb
